{"tid":1589702,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"著名bot<無人格=01 (b612星人)>再瘋狂洗版妨礙討論","createTime":"2019-09-23T11:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T09:27:22.000Z","uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3087b3ba9f507bdd2a40071de87a3349d23bc79a","tid":1589702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"&quot;無人格=01&quot;  (前稱&quot;B612星人&quot;) 被我正式投訴洗版兼貼fake news後, 本來有改善.  (貼fake news大圖只貼一次)<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1443384/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1443384/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n但最近佢故態復萌, 再不斷係短時間內重覆貼相同fake news大圖洗版, 妨礙其他版友既視線同討論.  我係三日前已經警告佢如果佢再咁做, 我會投訴佢.<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1581585/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1581585/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n結果, 佢<strong>今日變本加厲</strong>, 係短時間內重覆貼相同fake news大圖三次, 妨礙其他版友既視線同討論. <br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1589540/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1589540/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1ae486ad8592e224374b0293296e762f88d5d569","tid":1589702,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"07f5dd38e7becbfcc11392573cfc88944c2bb4d7","tid":1589702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"Bot洗版嚴重影響討論質素, 唔少連登仔都有投訴.<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1585068/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1585068/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1588415/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1588415/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1583204/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1583204/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1584144/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1584144/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n &quot;無人格=01 (B612星人)&quot;就係其中一位影響連登討論質素既bot,  我俾佢不斷狙擊洗版, 佢今日仲發展到係短時間內重覆貼相同fake news大圖三次去洗版同妨礙討論!    根本係刻意剝奪我既出post權利!"},{"pid":"eed680f0099aef12e93532c0f3f619e8545bb731","tid":1589702,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"網軍啦明顯，拖隻5毛出去斬"},{"pid":"f0f4d4a6faaf86902e0c66414f842a6f63e905b2","tid":1589702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"之前已經有另一連登人因為重覆貼相信內容洗版而被罰， 請求admin繼續罰為重覆貼相信內容洗版既bot. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (<strong>對唔住， 一篇文分三part貼， 因為一次過貼就&ldquo;遇到未知問題&rdquo;貼唔到</strong>）:-)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/492649/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/492649/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6c65dc3474f03528d97f74f3f8ba3802717277ea","tid":1589702,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed680f0099aef12e93532c0f3f619e8545bb731","tid":1589702,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"網軍啦明顯，拖隻5毛出去斬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"最麻煩係佢果D圖咁撚大, 貼一次就全世界都睇到<br />\n<br />\n而家仲要重覆貼相同大圖三次, 已經唔係表達意見, 而係刻意妨礙其他版友既視線同討論. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9d1b10e62e021482a1e2aada4155be04978366","tid":1589702,"uid":193215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bf8db140